sources.title: Captain Z-Ro - Christopher Columbus
sources.description: Episode 1 of the syndicated filmed series. Captain Z-Ro uses his time machine to protect humankind at various junctions in history. Public domain status: Registered as a published film 25 June 1955(LP11103). Not renewed. Subsequent copyright re-registration rejected in 1985: Captain Z-Ro/Christopher Columbus.
